job.title: RPSC SI & Platoon Commander Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 859 Vacancies in Rajasthan
job.body:
Total vacancies:859

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Sub Inspector AP (TSP & Non TSP) - 746
  • Sub Inspector IB (TSP) - 01
  • Sub Inspector IB (Non TSP) - 63
  • Platoon Commander (Non TSP) - 38
  • Sub Inspector MBC (TSP) - 11

Description

Latest Rajasthan Government Jobs for all graduates have been published by Rajasthan Public Service Commission for Platoon Commander vacancies in Rajasthan. If you are searching for a government job in Rajasthan then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Platoon Commander, from 09-02-2021, and till the last date. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Rajasthan and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee

  • Mode of application is Online
  • The application fee for General/ EWS/ BC/ OBC candidates is only 350/-
  • For OBC, BC Candidates of Rajasthan State: Rs. 250/- 
  • For SC/ ST/ PH Candidates: Rs. 150/-.

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Platoon Commander vacancies in Rajasthan, your graduation must be completed from a recognized University
  • Working knowledge of Hindi written in Devnagri Script and knowledge of Rajasthani Culture.

Important dates

  • New Online Dates for EWS Candidates:
  • Starting Date to Apply Online: 09-06-2021
  • Last Date to Apply Online & Payment of Fee: 23-06-2021 by 12:00 Hrs

Age Limit Criteria

  • Minimum Age Limit: 20 Years
  • Maximum Age Limit: 25 Years
  • Age Relaxation is Applicable as per Rules

RPSC Platoon Commander Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the Rajasthan Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is ₹ 35,400.

How to apply for RPSC SI & Platoon Commander Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the  Platoon Commander. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of RPSC and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by RPSC
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
